user_permission.name: ADMIN
user_permission.description: This permission confers administrative privileges to its owner.

user_permission.name: USER_CREATOR
user_permission.description: This permission allows a user to create other users

user_permission.name: ACB_ADMIN
user_permission.description: This permission gives a user write access to their ACBs.

user_permission.name: ACB_STAFF
user_permission.description: This permission gives a user read access to their ACBs

user_permission.name: ATL_ADMIN
user_permission.description: This permission gives a user write access to their ATLs.

user_permission.name: ATL_STAFF
user_permission.description: This permission gives a user read access to their ATLs.

user_permission.name: CMS_STAFF
user_permission.description: This permission gives a user read access to CMS reports.

user_permission.name: ONC_STAFF
user_permission.description: This permission gives a user access to the CMS Download file and report navigation section. It denies editing of Users/Products/CPs/ACBs/etc. No user invitation ability.
